  "text": "The study was approved by the institutional committee for human investigation at our hospital. The database of earlier investigations [CITATION_1] was evaluated. Technicians carrying out the HUTT measurements did not know of the intention to compare between the groups; subsequent analysis of charts was done by outside investigators who were unaware of the study's intention.",
